    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready for a car that's genuinely dependable and well cared for? This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it starts up reliably every time, drives smoothly, and has been maintained with real attention over the years. The interior is clean and comfortable, and the exterior presents nicely with only the minor wear you'd expect from a well-used but well-loved car. No surprises here \u2014 just solid, everyday reliability at a fair price!",
